  • public class AbstractMatchedPairsFilterNodeModel
extends org.knime.core.node.NodeModel
    Abstract Class for filtering by fragmentability according to a specified fragmentation Schema. The class can be subclassed to give either filter (1 output port) or splitter (2 output port) variants

    s.roughley <knime@vernalis.com>
